Package me.tazadejava.mission

Main package that handles all mission-related classes and its run-time logistics.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Mission
    Holds all data related to a particular mission.
    MissionCommandHandler
    Command manager that allows the player to start commands (particularly, start the mission) and other various options.
    MissionEventListener
    Tracks player actions while the mission is active to store into stats.
    MissionGraph
    Class holding the graphical representation of a mission map with room and decision vertices.
    MissionGraph.MissionVertex  
    MissionManager
    Handles a mission active/inactive state, as well as the mission logistics overall (including countdown).
    MissionRoom
    Represents a room on a map.
    WorldManager
    Helper class that will autoload worlds that were not part of the original worlds (typically world, world_nether, world_end).
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    MissionGraph.MissionVertexType
